    <title>CodeTogether</title>
    <link>http://marketplace.eclipse.org/content/codetogether</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-resource-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; src=&quot;http://marketplace.eclipse.org/sites/default/files/codetogether-full-logo.png&quot; width=&quot;110&quot; height=&quot;80&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-shared-date-updated field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Date Updated:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Mon, 2020-11-02 16:00&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/search/content/%22Genuitec%2C%20LLC%22&quot;&gt;Genuitec, LLC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-shared-date-created field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Date Created:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Thu, 2020-03-05 15:48&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-shared-submitted-by field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Submitted by:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/user/twebbcke/listings&quot; title=&quot;Tim Webb&quot;&gt;Tim Webb&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now with IDE to IDE support and same-file simultaneous editing! Add &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.codetogether.com/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;CodeTogether&lt;/a&gt; to Eclipse for pair programming from anywhere. Great for remote teams, even when using different IDEs. CodeTogether is available for Eclipse, IntelliJ and VS Code. You can host a collaborative session from any supported IDE, and participants can join from their preferred IDE or a browser.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Source is always &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.codetogether.com/download/security/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;End-to-End Encrypted&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.codetogether.com/docs/on-premises-faq&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;on-premises&lt;/a&gt; hosting is optionally available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Host-based intelligence ensures everyone gets the language smarts needed for capabilities such as content assist and validation, regardless of how they join the session.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Getting Started&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Simply &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.codetogether.com/docs/codetogether-for-eclipse-installation&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;install the plugin&lt;/a&gt;, start a session, and share the URL with your peers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Starting a Session&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click Host New Session from the CodeTogether view or right-click in the editor and select Start Hosting Session.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Inviting Users to a Session&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click Copy Invite URL in the CodeTogether view to copy the session URL to the clipboard, and then share it with others. Participants simply click Join Remote Session in the CodeTogether view of their IDE, or paste the URL into any modern browser.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information, see the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.codetogether.com/docs/getting-started-with-codetogether/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Getting Started Guide&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
