    <title>Aspose.BarCode (Maven) Java for Eclipse</title>
    <link>http://marketplace.eclipse.org/content/asposebarcode-maven-java-eclipse</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-resource-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; src=&quot;http://marketplace.eclipse.org/sites/default/files/aspose_barcode-for-java.png&quot; width=&quot;80&quot; height=&quot;80&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-shared-date-updated field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Date Updated:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Mon, 2020-11-02 10:47&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/search/content/%22Aspose%20Pty%20Ltd%22&quot;&gt;Aspose Pty Ltd&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-shared-date-created field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Date Created:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Tue, 2020-10-27 14:36&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-shared-submitted-by field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Submitted by:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/user/amarketplace/listings&quot; title=&quot;Aspose Marketplace&quot;&gt;Aspose Marketplace&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Java Barcode &amp;amp; QR Library&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://products.aspose.com/barcode/java&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Aspose.BarCode for Java&lt;/a&gt; provides a complete framework to control almost everything about barcodes. It includes Barcode Recognition Engine that can be fine-tuned for performance &amp;amp; accuracy, as well as a Barcode Creator that can render barcode labels in different image format, dimensions, resolution or appearances. Check out the &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.aspose.com/barcode/java/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;documentation&lt;/a&gt; if you wish to read more about the Java Barcode Library.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Aspose.Words Java (Maven) for Eclipse&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Aspose.BarCode Maven Project (wizard)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Creates a Maven project to use Aspose.BarCode for Java. Please follow New -&amp;gt; Project -&amp;gt; Maven-&amp;gt; Aspose.BarCode Maven Project.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Aspose.BarCode Code Example (wizard)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Copies the downloaded Code Examples into your project for you to get started. Please follow New -&amp;gt; Other -&amp;gt; Java -&amp;gt; Aspose.BarCode Code Example.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;NOTE: Selected Code Examples will be copied under &quot;com.aspose.barcode.examples&quot; package. Required resources will be copied to the corresponding directory within &quot;src/main/resources&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Other Features&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Supported with the latest version of Eclipse IDE.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compatible with Mac, Linux and Windows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open Source&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://products.aspose.com/barcode/java&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Product Page&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.aspose.com/barcode/java/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Docs&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://products.aspose.app/barcode/family&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Demos&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://apireference.aspose.com/barcode/java&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;API Reference&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/aspose-barcode/Aspose.BarCode-for-Java/tree/master/Examples&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Examples&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.aspose.com/category/barcode/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Blog&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://forum.aspose.com/c/barcode&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Free Support&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://purchase.aspose.com/temporary-license&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Temporary License&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
