  <item>
    <title>Jmr Code Generator for Java, JavaEE, SpringBoot/SpringCloud, JavaScript, React/Vue/Angular</title>
    <link>http://marketplace.eclipse.org/content/jmr-code-generator-java-javaee-springbootspringcloud-javascript-reactvueangular</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-resource-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; src=&quot;http://marketplace.eclipse.org/sites/default/files/jmr_logo2.png&quot; width=&quot;72&quot; height=&quot;72&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-shared-date-updated field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Date Updated:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Fri, 2020-10-30 13:25&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/search/content/%22JmrTeam%22&quot;&gt;JmrTeam&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-shared-date-created field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Date Created:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Wed, 2017-08-02 23:41&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-shared-submitted-by field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Submitted by:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/user/yuxinwork/listings&quot; title=&quot;Xin Yu&quot;&gt;Xin Yu&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Developers can use the template(JSP-like) to generate any kind of language(Java, JavaScript, Python, PHP, etc.).  Any kind of framework(JavaEE, springboot/springCloud/springMVC，ReactJS/VueJS/AngularJS, JQuery，hibernate, ibatis/mybatis, struts/struts2, JPA etc.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now Support Eclipse and Intellij IDEA is under development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Such as, it&#039;s possible to &lt;strong&gt;generate CRUD&lt;/strong&gt; in a few minutes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Template:&lt;/strong&gt; Support Java Script( &amp;lt;%%&amp;gt; JSP-like ) and Jmr Tag(set/get/for...)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Model:&lt;/strong&gt; Database Model(like Table/View), Java POJO Model, Xml File Model and includes&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Transform/Mapping/Convert Tool&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Action: &lt;/strong&gt;A Java Class can set Java variables to template.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GitHub:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/JmrTeam/generator&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/JmrTeam/generator&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documenation Page:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.jmr-source.com/doc/en/index.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.jmr-source.com/doc/en/index.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Change Log：&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;JET2project is no longer needed and will not be generated.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;----------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jmr是一款可以使用Jet模板（类似JSP语法）生成代码的插件，支持任何语言(Java, JavaScript, Html, Python, PHP等)和任何框架(JavaEE, springboot/springCloud/springMVC，ReactJS/VueJS/AngularJS, JQuery，hibernate, ibatis/mybatis,struts/struts2, JPA等)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;目前Eclipse插件版本1.5.0。Intellij IDEA插件正在开发中...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jmr不受语言和框架的限制，可以自由生成任何想要的代码，比如用它轻松的生成增删查改的代码。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GitHub:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/JmrTeam/generator&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/JmrTeam/generator&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;中文文档: &lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.jmr-source.com/doc/zh/index.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.jmr-source.com/doc/zh/index.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
